# Code style conventions used in this repository #

Upper Camel Case (e.g. BitException)
	- Classes
	- Namespaces
	
Lower Camel Case (e.g. compressFiles(..) )
	- Class methods
	
Apps Hungarian Notation (e.g. mFormat)
	- Class variables
	- Local variables

C Notation (e.g. out_archive)
	- Methods/Functions arguments
	- Functions outside classes
	
All Caps (e.g. DEFAULT_DLL)
	- Preprocessor defines
	
